\begin_layout Standard
Given these values (zeros for the empty boxes), our left hand side is 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{A}\left(aX+bY\right)=\left(-3+3i+j-k,-3-i+3j-3k\right)$
\end_inset

 and right hand side 
\begin_inset Formula $aL_{A}(X)+bL_{A}(Y)=\left(-1+5i-j-k,-5-3i+j+k\right)$
\end_inset

